title.en: Gimai ga Seijo dakara to Konyakuhaki Saremashita ga, Watashi wa Yousei no Itoshigo desu
Kawaii Gimai ga Konyakuhaki Saretarashii no de, Ima kara "Orei" ni Mairimasu
Kizoku kara Shomin ni Natta no de, Kon'yaku o Kaishou Saremashita!
Watashi no Konyakusha-sama no Dokuzetsu ga Sugiru ~Minna ni Shio Taiou no Hazu ga Watashi wa Dekiai Sareteimasu~
Migawari Konyaku Shananoni, Gin Ookami Heika ga Doushitemo Hanashite Kuremasen!
Denka, Anata ga Suteta Onna ga Honmono no Seijo desu
Seijo no Ane desu ga, Naze ka Miwaku no Koushaku-sama ni Tsukaeru Koto ni narimashita
Enzai Reijou wa Shinjitai - Ginpatsu ga Fukitsu to Iwarete Konyaku Hakisareta Shishaku Reijou wa Ansatsu Kizoku ni Dekiaisarete Daini no Jinsei wo Tannou suru you desu
Honmono no Seijo Janai to Bareta no ni, Outei Denka ni Semararete imasu
Kinou made Namae mo Yonde Kurenakatta Koushaku-sama ga, Kyuu ni Dekiai shitekuru no desu ga?
Kono Ai wa, Kokuou Heika no Gomeirei Janai - Ohitori-sama Kibou no Reijou desu ga, Funaka na Kishi ga Hanashitekuremasen!
Doumo, Akuyaku ni Sareta Reijou desukeredo
Watashi, Seijo. Ima, Kankinsarete Iru no
Konyaku Haki Shita Aite ga Mainichi Shazai ni Kimasu ga, Fukuen Nante Zettai ni Ariemasen!
Konyaku Haki wo Shita Reijou wa Gaman wo Tomemashita
